Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.71,0:01:04.08,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I have the perfect name for her, Aelita.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.71,0:01:04.08,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我有一个完美的名字 Aelita
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.70,0:01:20.03,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Oh my God look at her Waldo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.70,0:01:20.03,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}哦 我的天哪 看看她 Waldo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.79,0:01:23.54,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}She's so so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.79,0:01:23.54,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}她真是太漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.38,0:01:26.65,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Well she is just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.38,0:01:26.65,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}恩 她就像你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:30.59,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}She will be a princess when she grows up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:30.59,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}她长大后会成为一个公主
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.06,0:01:33.13,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}She will have the perfect life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.06,0:01:33.13,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}她会有完美的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:48.61,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Aelita just fell asleep and the terrible snowstorm just started.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:48.61,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Aelita刚刚睡着 而可怕的暴风雪刚刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.41,0:01:51.30,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}What are you working on, dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.41,0:01:51.30,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你在做什么 亲爱的？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.06,0:01:54.62,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I just bought an old factory in France.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.06,0:01:54.62,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我刚刚在法国买了一个旧工厂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.29,0:01:57.46,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Oh sounds great but why.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.29,0:01:57.46,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}哦 听起来不错 但为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.14,0:02:00.66,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}To invest in our daughter's future.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.14,0:02:00.66,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为了给我们女儿的未来投资
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.75,0:02:06.73,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Waldo please tell me this isn't about project Carthage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.75,0:02:06.73,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Waldo 请告诉我这不是有关迦太基项目的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:10.31,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Waldo don't you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:10.31,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Waldo 你不要去那里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.65,0:02:11.98,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You know they are dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.65,0:02:11.98,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你知道他们很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:14.79,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You saw everything with your own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:14.79,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你亲眼看到了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:19.10,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Please. Please you have to promise me to stay away from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:19.10,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}求你了 求你了 你得答应我离他们远一点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.86,0:02:21.17,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.86,0:02:21.17,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}求你了
