Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.61,0:02:23.65,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我知道他们有多危险
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:25.12,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I won't get near them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:25.12,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我不会靠近他们的
