Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:27.18,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没有必要担心这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.23,0:02:28.43,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Please calm down.
