Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.45,0:05:02.38,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}哇 但我们为什么要去那里？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:05.94,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Because today we will skate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:05.94,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为今天我们要滑冰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.48,0:05:10.24,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}What but I don't know how to skate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.48,0:05:10.24,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什么 但我不知道如何滑冰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.34,0:05:14.06,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And that's exactly why we are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.34,0:05:14.06,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而这正是我们来这里的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:19.90,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Aelita, darling slow down wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:19.90,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Aelita 亲爱的 慢点 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:23.50,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Aelita just be careful in the ice okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:23.50,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Aelita 在冰上要小心 好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.54,0:05:24.36,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'm worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.54,0:05:24.36,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我很担心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.54,0:05:26.74,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Okay mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.54,0:05:26.74,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好的 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.62,0:05:30.66,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Let's get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.62,0:05:30.66,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}让我们准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.64,0:05:48.53,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I want to skate like mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.64,0:05:48.53,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我想像妈妈一样滑冰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.48,0:05:53.82,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}She's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.48,0:05:53.82,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}她真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:58.09,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Yeah she's very good with it indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:58.09,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是的 事实上她非常擅长滑冰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:02.05,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}whoo what can I do to skate like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:02.05,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喔 我怎么做才能像她那样滑冰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.97,0:06:06.30,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Well you have to train a lot and every day too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.97,0:06:06.30,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}恩 你必须经常训练 而且每天都要训练
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.82,0:06:09.88,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Like with my piano lessons?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.82,0:06:09.88,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就像我的钢琴课一样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.94,0:06:14.94,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Yes sweetheart like with the piano lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.94,0:06:14.94,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是的 亲爱的 就像上钢琴课一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:29.62,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}That was awesome darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:29.62,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那真是太棒了 亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.75,0:06:30.95,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Very well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.75,0:06:30.95,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}很好 那么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:36.10,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}gorgeous and perfect as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:36.10,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}华丽而完美 像往常一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.57,0:06:39.06,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.57,0:06:39.06,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.47,0:06:40.52,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Now let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.47,0:06:40.52,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}现在我们回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.94,0:06:45.76,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Best day ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.94,0:06:45.76,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有史以来最好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.94,0:06:55.30,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Well if you like it so much, we can come here more often.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.94,0:06:55.30,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好吧 如果你这么喜欢的话 我们可以经常来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.80,0:07:06.92,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Look at my giant snowball mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.80,0:07:06.92,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}看看我的大雪球妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.35,0:07:08.98,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Stay near the house, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.35,0:07:08.98,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}呆在房子附近 亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.42,0:07:15.89,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Well then my angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.42,0:07:15.89,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好吧 我的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.49,0:07:19.09,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}What's that someone Waldo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.49,0:07:19.09,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那是什么 Waldo？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:29.76,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I think it's a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:29.76,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我想是一辆车
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:39.01,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Mommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:39.01,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:42.23,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Waldo what's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:42.23,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Waldo 发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:44.06,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Go protect Aelita.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:44.06,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}去保护Aelita
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.74,0:07:46.72,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Here they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.74,0:07:46.72,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:48.46,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}What should we do with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:48.46,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我们该怎么处理他们？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.27,0:07:52.66,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Get the woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.27,0:07:52.66,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}抓住那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:54.55,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:54.55,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:07:56.48,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Over my dead body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:07:56.48,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}想都别想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:59.68,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Huh why not? Fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:59.68,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}呵 吃我一拳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:05.60,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}No please. Waldo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:05.60,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Waldo 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:13.30,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Did you really think we wouldn't find out who's bought that old factory?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:13.30,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你真的认为我们不会发现是谁买了那个旧工厂吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.66,0:08:16.30,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}We knew that you would attack project Carthage
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.66,0:08:16.30,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我们知道你会攻击迦太基项目
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:18.56,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and now we will pay with your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:18.56,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而现在我们就要用你的生命来偿还
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.24,0:08:20.02,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Waldo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.24,0:08:20.02,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Waldo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.58,0:08:22.59,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.58,0:08:22.59,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.22,0:08:23.97,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.22,0:08:23.97,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.12,0:08:26.76,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Say goodbye to your family Waldo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.12,0:08:26.76,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}跟你的家人说再见吧 Waldo
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.95,0:08:30.92,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.95,0:08:30.92,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:34.77,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}What? Why? I want to kill this traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:34.77,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什么？为什么？我想杀了这个叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:37.89,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}He must suffer while he's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:37.89,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他只有在活着的时候才会受苦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:40.02,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Death is an easy escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:40.02,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}死亡是个容易逃脱的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.57,0:08:43.69,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Fine. don't forget this Franz.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.57,0:08:43.69,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好吧 别忘了这个 Franz
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.78,0:08:48.65,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}If you try to attack project Carthage again, you'll never see your daughter as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.78,0:08:48.65,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果你再试图攻击迦太基项目 你也将见不到你的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.39,0:08:51.58,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Come on. Let's not waste time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.39,0:08:51.58,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}来吧 让我们不要再浪费时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.64,0:08:53.82,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Enough chitchat. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.64,0:08:53.82,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}闲聊够了 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.62,0:08:58.44,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Very well until next time, Waldo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.62,0:08:58.44,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}很好 后会有期 Waldo
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:07.49,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Mommy! Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:07.49,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妈妈 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:13.14,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Please, please, stop the car, Aelita!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:13.14,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}求你了 求你了 把车停下来 Aelita
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:15.54,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Aelita!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:15.54,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Aelita
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:21.10,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:21.10,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妈妈
